Sheffield Wall type combined cooker mounted and cantilevered on stainless steel paneled columns with in-built gas and electrical services.

Unit is custom designed to have various cooking range including low pressure & high pressure burners, griddle, grill, fryer and any additional customized cooking equipment.

Optional features for combined cookers include:- spine/ hood mounting columns / stainless steel heavy duty central overshelf mounted on 75 dia circular tube / stainless steel tubular water tap / salamander mounting brackets)
